title: Packaging technical analysis
text:
1 Introduction
Technical analysis of database composed of the summary reports of laboratory testing for containers, all containers are different but the analysis are common to all of them, the expected result is to find patterns and insights that help to define the container features, classify the container based on them and connect those features to the laboratory results. I worked as packaging engineer 5 years and I’m familiar with the data collected in this technical database, and want to proof through viauls analysis the behavior of containers I know by experience.

title: 2  Data
text:
2.1 Missing value analysis
database with collection of data features - laboratory results, the features include: volume, dimensions, design and laboratory results will be masked appearing as test1, test2 etc. The analysis will not disclose the real data and insights but will show visually all the patterns and insights if they exist. ## Description
